dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents airports in the United States, Puerto Rico, and U.S. Virgin Islands with airport passenger enplanements of 25 passengers or more per year. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2. U.S. National Atlas Airports provides information about the locations, names, location identifiers, and enplanements of airports for conducting geographic analysis on national and large regional scales. National Atlas of the United States, ESRI and U.S. Geological Survey. (2014). United States National Atlas Airports, 2010-2012. ESRI.
dc_creator_sm: National Atlas of the United States
